  "abstract": "Groundnuts after harvest are attacked by a plethora of insect pests in storage\r\nacross the world. This publication discusses the importance of post-harvest\r\nprocessing in the management of insect pests. Emphasis is given to crop\r\nhusbandry, monitoring, sampling, prevention of insect damage, management\r\nof established infestation, and eco-friendly management in commercial and\r\nfarm-household situations. This bulletin also discusses various practices\r\nsuitable for commercial and household storage",
